title: Fox Mtb Trip Nor Cal Part 2 Anthony Messere / Kirt Voreis
description: We did some filming and testing with the new 2012 product line in Nor Cal. Here is some more fun footage we got of Anthony and Kirt riding together. The new 2012 Fox Bike line will be dropping 2/1/2012. Keep an eye out for it!
